		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Mapper 11 seems to be a really wierd one.
<br />
<br />I got a NES ROM image that is mapper 11, and works in all emulators.  But no matter what donor board I use (that is a mapper 11) the game is all messed up.

		

